'''Lunar New Year''' is a recurring limited-time promotion by [[VRChat]] tied to the [[wikipedia:Lunar New Year|Lunar New Year]]. Each year's promotion is themed around the corresponding [[wikipedia:Chinese zodiac|zodiac]] animal and has included free cosmetic content such as [[Special:MyLanguage/Stickers|stickers]], and, from 2026 onward, paid [[Special:MyLanguage/Shop|Shop]] listings.

