=== Lunar New Year 2025 ===
''Main article: [[Lunar New Year 2025]]''

'''Lunar New Year 2025''' marked the Year of the Snake. The promotion consisted only of a free limited-time sticker set; no paid [[Special:MyLanguage/Shop|Shop]] items were released for it.

=== Lunar New Year 2026 ===
''Main article: [[Lunar New Year 2026]]''

'''Lunar New Year 2026''' marked the Year of the Horse and was the first Lunar New Year promotion to include purchasable Shop items, including a [[Special:MyLanguage/Portals|portal]], a [[Special:MyLanguage/Warp Effects|warp effect]], three [[Special:MyLanguage/Items|items]], a premium [[Special:MyLanguage/Emojis|emoji]] bundle, and a holographic [[Special:MyLanguage/Stickers|sticker]] pack. A free [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+|VRC+]]-exclusive "Lucky Red Envelope" [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat Credits|credit]] bundle was also offered.<ref name="lny2026-yt"/>

